For adapting into multiple ETF history provider we need to refactor the current history fetching.
The history providers should take a TrackerConfig (etf symbol, history symbol, conversion symbol) and output a map where the key is week/year and the value is € value of one share
The frontend should offer a option to configure which history provider to use.

The first one should be the existing Yahoo one
A new second one should be solactive:

